data.description: Five bedrooms, three bathrooms, No HOA, over 2,000 finished SF and an oversized three car garage in the lovely town of Elkhart, just outside of Ankeny! Many updates throughout including a recent basement finish which features two bedrooms a full bath and living area all downstairs! Newer SS kitchen appliances, and LVP flooring throughout. Backyard is completely fenced in for plenty of privacy when entertaining guests or sitting out by the firepit.  Be ready to relax on the patio or enjoy the sunny days lounging or grilling on the large rear deck, overlooking the fully fenced backyard. Garage is a dream, plenty of room for all your enclosed parking needs plus storage and workshop space if desired. Located in a charming smaller neighborhood, this home combines the serenity of suburban living with the convenience of being just a short drive away from highly sought after amenities. With its thoughtful design and modern finishes, 310 NE Allison Ave is ready to welcome you home. It is a short commute from Des Moines and close to Interstate 35 for easy commutes anywhere in the metro. Ankeny is right next door for all your shopping, entertainment and dining needs.
